00:36:56,920 --> 00:36:58,080
Hindi.

462
00:36:58,920 --> 00:37:01,240
Iniisip ko lang yung taong naka-itim
ay masyadong malakas.

463
00:37:01,840 --> 00:37:03,160
Kahit magkasama, hindi namin sila kayang talunin.

464
00:37:04,400 --> 00:37:06,640
Commander Li, bukod kay Ji Ling,

465
00:37:06,720 --> 00:37:09,000
