513
00:40:43,920 --> 00:40:45,120
Saan siya nakatira?

514
00:40:49,160 --> 00:40:50,200
naalala ko na!

515
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:51,360
Tinakot mo ako.

516
00:40:51,440 --> 00:40:53,440
Ang manuscript!
Ang unang kabanata ng manuskrito na iyon

517
00:40:54,040 --> 00:40:55,480
ay kuwento ni Little Pomegranate.

518
00:40:56,000 --> 00:40:58,040
Sa sandaling narinig ko ang mga salita
"Munting Pomegranate",

519
00:40:58,560 --> 00:41:01,120
Parang nakita ko na sila
sa isang lugar kanina.

520
00:41:02,200 --> 00:41:04,680
"Ang Dakilang Demonyo at Munting Granada."

521
00:41:04,760 --> 00:41:06,080
Anong klaseng sulatin ito?

522
00:41:06,160 --> 00:41:07,120
Napakapangit.

523
00:41:07,640 --> 00:41:10,640
Baluktot ang sulat-kamay.
Ito ay pangit.

524
00:41:12,440 --> 00:41:13,440
Panget talaga.

525
00:41:14,560 --> 00:41:16,440
Ngunit gayon pa man, nakilala ko ang mga salita
"Little" at "Pomegranate".

526
00:41:17,080 --> 00:41:18,000
Ngunit

527
00:41:18,680 --> 00:41:20,080
Napakaayos ng sulat-kamay ni Mu Long.

528
00:41:20,160 --> 00:41:21,400
Paano ito magiging baluktot?

529
00:41:22,440 --> 00:41:23,680
Masyado siyang nainom.

530
00:41:23,760 --> 00:41:25,040
Isara ito.

531
00:41:48,760 --> 00:41:51,080
Maliit na Pomegranate.

532
00:41:57,680 --> 00:41:58,880
Maliit na Pomegranate?

533
00:41:58,960 --> 00:42:01,160
Bakit ang Little Pomegranate
parang umiiyak sya?

534
00:42:05,400 --> 00:42:06,800
Hindi ba si Wangyan yan?

535
00:42:16,280 --> 00:42:17,320
Ito…

536
00:42:18,280 --> 00:42:19,440
Ito talaga ako.

537
00:42:21,360 --> 00:42:23,440
Pero bakit ako nasa painting na ito?

538
00:42:24,560 --> 00:42:26,840
At yung matangkad at gwapong lalaki sa likod

539
00:42:27,600 --> 00:42:28,520
ay si Mr. Yan.

540
00:42:29,560 --> 00:42:31,680
Ang pintor ay si Cui Jun.

541
00:42:33,640 --> 00:42:34,480
Sino si Cui Jun?

542
00:42:36,480 --> 00:42:37,440
Baka

543
00:42:38,680 --> 00:42:39,600
May pwede akong subukan.

544
00:43:04,280 --> 00:43:05,320
Saan nagpunta sina Wu Shiguang at Wangyan?

545
00:43:05,400 --> 00:43:06,840
Paano sila nawala
sa isang kisap mata?

546
00:43:08,360 --> 00:43:09,880
Pumasok na sila sa painting.

547
00:43:10,480 --> 00:43:11,360
Bakit nila ako iniwan?

548
00:43:12,360 --> 00:43:13,280
Anong magandang gagawin mo?

549
00:43:13,360 --> 00:43:14,880
Anong magandang gagawin ko?

550
00:43:14,960 --> 00:43:15,800
Naisip ko na.

551
00:43:17,120 --> 00:43:19,320
Ang babaeng nasa painting
ay Little Pomegranate.

552
00:43:19,400 --> 00:43:21,800
At ang kwentong ito ay dapat na mayroon
may kinalaman kay Mr. Yan.

553
00:43:21,880 --> 00:43:23,520
Tungkol naman sa dakilang demonyo,

554
00:43:24,040 --> 00:43:26,360
